{"arkId":"cl010097268","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097268","modified ":"2025-11-03","title":"Montre \u00e0 bo\u00eetier ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre \u00e0 bo\u00eetier ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1585 - 1600","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1585,"endYear":1600,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 687","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le bo\u00eetier est compos\u00e9 de deux couvercles d\u00e9cor\u00e9s d\u0027un bas-relief. L\u0027un repr\u00e9sente Mars et V\u00e9nus, l\u0027autre V\u00e9nus et Adonis. Le pourtour est orn\u00e9, en bas-relief, de deux mascarons, de feuilles et d\u0027\u00e9pis. Le pendant, de forme ovale, grav\u00e9, laisse passer un anneau de suspension. A l\u0027oppos\u00e9, une perle piriforme est suspendue.\r\nBronze cisel\u00e9 et dor\u00e9.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"9,9","displayDimension":"9,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"not